init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: When the #1 Dad mug changed, my street was of two minds.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Most of the men that were in the top ten on my street, decided that they would be #1 and began strutting down the street like ro

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: At least this was better than our previous ranking system, when we just made up a number to represent the ranking of a dad.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: My neighbor was a dad and he had always ranked around eight out of ten.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Mario would make rules and order people around like they were his personal slaves.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He woke up the next day, ready to see how well this plan went off.
